 part c)
 what are web sockets where it is used.
 ANswer===
 The WebSocket protocol enables interaction between a web browser (or other client application) and a web server
 Its allow both the server and the client to push messages at any time. Almost every borser supports Websockets
 also solve HTTP issues:-
                        )Full-duplex communication ----->  client and server can talk to each other independently(same time)
                        Bi-directional protocol:----> client/server can send a message to the other party

                       *) when connections are terminated  its can't recover automatically.we have to implement ourself


uses:

 Multiplayer games
 Multimedia Chats
 editing/coding
 Social feed
 Financial tickers

